R

register(Optional<String>, Optional<String>) - Static method in class com.google.crypto.tink.integration.gcpkms.GcpKmsClient
Deprecated.
It is preferable to not register KMS clients. Instead, create the GcpKmsClient yourself and call getAead to get a remote Aead. Use this Aead to encrypt a keyset with TinkProtoKeysetFormat.serializeEncryptedKeyset, or to create an envelope Aead using KmsEnvelopeAead.create.
